            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Pro salute Augustorum et <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>enatus</ex></expan> p<expan><ex>opuli</ex><abbr>q</abbr><ex>ue</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>R</abbr><ex>omani</ex></expan> et exercitus <lb n="3"/>Isidi Pantheae Claudia <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>iberta</ex></expan> Icmas <lb n="4"/>et Vitulus <expan><abbr>Caes</abbr><ex>aris</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>sacer</abbr><ex>dote</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Claud</abbr><ex>io</ex></expan> Attico <expan><abbr>lib</abbr><ex>erto</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Tabula ansata; in mehrere Fragmente gebrochen. Fundjahr: 1999-2001. Datierung: möglicherweise aus Anlass der Niederschlagung des Saturninus-Aufstandes 89 n. Chr. gesetzt.</p>
            </div>
